      • setCapturedVideoRotates

        public void setCapturedVideoRotates(boolean capturedVideoRotates)
        If set to true (the default), the orientation of captured video should follow the device orientation while streaming, otherwise the orientation that was active when streaming began should be maintained.
        Parameters:
        capturedVideoRotates - true> if the orientation of captured video should follow the device orientation while streaming, false> otherwise
